Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venus Games, round one, second match is Ryan versus Okamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their offense and defense are completely even!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's still too difficult to predict the outcome of this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lf it keeps going like this, l'll definitely lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l have to do it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here l come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one standing is Ayumi Okamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane Ryan has lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want you guys to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later! lf we're lucky, we'll fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have no plans to hang around for your sick show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:09.85,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hohoemu namida michibiku kaze wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears with a smile, the guiding wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:17.56,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yasashii nioi nareta nukumori{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A gentle scent, your warmth seems so familiar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.96,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima kagiri aru sekai to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ln such a limited world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.13,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kuusai no hate ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}beyond the skies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.40,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kanjyou tabane hitomi wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your eyes are full of emotion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:33.10,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}nani o mitsukeru darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what will they find?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.50,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mienai hoshi kokoro nokoshi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A star l can't see, leaving my heart behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.00,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}saten no sora e to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to the satin skies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.40,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kikoenu you ni mienu you ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be sure they can't hear, be sure they can't see,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.80,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}chiisaku hakisuteta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}say it softly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:10.71,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima naraba mabayui kako utte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now you can shoot your bright past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:14.12,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yuganda sora mo tsumetai yoru mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twisted mornings, cold nights,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.35,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}genseki ni kaeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}turn them into gemstones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.32,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}utsuro na namida yurusareru nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears with an empty look, if it can be forgiven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:31.23,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kono mama zutto mamoraretetai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l want to stay like this, l want you to protect me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.67,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima hosoi hari ga hitotsu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just now a thin needle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.83,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}toki oikoshiteku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...pierced through time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.11,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yagate bokura no ue ni mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dawn will come soon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:46.78,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}asahi wa noboru darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the part we've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only brought this many to fuck me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's try to make this fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want to fuck me, just try it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but be prepared to lose an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a little more gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect to satisfy a woman like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt... lt hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the eighth contestant has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misty from Hanna Miller's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's her ring name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent for the semi-finals match has been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She completely overpowered Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a DVD of the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. lt's only up to where she won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess it's okay if you want to sulk like that. lt's up to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at this rate, you'll definitely lose the semi-finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you lose, Sanari's sacrifice will have been in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to go fight Anna now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l plan to do everything in my power to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, if l lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l made it specifically for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Venus Games! This is the third match of round one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the red corner, Anna Fairgold from Propaganda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the blue corner, Kei Sagara from Petit Panini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l made it specifically for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She made it for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would Kei do that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no ordinary technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okamoto! Such incredible speed! lt's absolutely divine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last one standing is Ayumi Okamoto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diane Ryan has lost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of strategy should l use?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either way, l need to catch her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l'll watch it from the beginning again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuu, are you watching?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l wonder when you'll see this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before or after the match?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am l there with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this point, l have no idea how my match against Anna will go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:13:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but, if l lose... Yuu, you're the only one who can stop her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have incredible power and potential within you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who called you here believes that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why you're fighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle isn't for you or Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lt's all for his selfish desires.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anna will probably defeat me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and l doubt l'll be spared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuu, please! Defeat Anna Fairgold!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's turning into a monster...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stop her path of destruction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l believe in you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, if l lose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victor is Anna Fairgold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei Sagara is unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...l'm leaving the rest in your hands, Yuu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. The match is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The penalty is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they throw you in a cell if you lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures, since it's an illegal competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder how the matches are going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l bet Yuu's next opponent has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Sanari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! l told you not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, what's happening in the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Yuu's next opponent? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls something wrong, Masaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know... that Anna Fairgold is Yuu's twin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Yuu, she's also your clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki, right? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know who l am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not on the guest list. Are you going to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you going to torture me to make me confess, and then kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt might be fun to tear you apart in front of Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'm not going to kill you or turn you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf something were to happen to you, Yuu would be heavily distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you wanted to beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not about wanting to win. l will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l especially want to beat Yuu when she's desperate to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, l already know your story,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's really no point in torturing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You teamed up with the Original, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To save Yuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys share a mutual interest so working together makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Original?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call her. Yuka Takeuchi, also known as Misty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna... Who are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew... Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No big reason really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll be fighting our little sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why l came.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can all be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can all...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your little sisters, but they're also my little sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and while they're fighting right now, l'm going to make them into a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln order to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Round one, fourth match!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the red corner, representing May Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yung Ching Jyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the blue corner, representing Hanna Miller's!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misty! Misty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l'm leaving the rest in your hands, Yuu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.39,0:24:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it! The mysterious Misty is moving on to the semi-finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.53,0:24:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you really? You?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.94,0:24:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l swear l'll have it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.01,0:24:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Winning is hard, but l can't lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l don't want to lose. l will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.31,0:24:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:25:02.70,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hohoemu namida michibiku kaze wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:25:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears with a smile, the guiding wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:10.40,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yasashii nioi nareta nukumori{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A gentle scent, your warmth seems so familiar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:13.84,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima kagiri aru sekai to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ln such a limited world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.93,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kuusai no hate ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}beyond the skies.{\i0}
