Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.24,0:25:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your eyes are full of emotion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:26.08,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}nani o mitsukeru darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what will they find?{\i0}
